"""Basic sets
set number "line numbers
set showmatch "highlight reciprocating parenthesis or bracket
set ruler "Show line, col on status line

"""Var sets
set mouse=a "enable mouse click on terminal window


"""Searching
set incsearch "Search as characters are entered
set hlsearch "Highlight matching cases

"""Tabs & Spaces
set tabstop=4 "changes the width of a TAB, as measured in spaces
set expandtab "Sets tabs to be expanded into tabstop number of spaces
set shiftwidth=4 "Changes indent to n number of spaces /indent
set softtabstop=4 "Backspacing after a TAB will remove n spaces /press


"""Syntax & Plug-ins
syntax on

"""look & feel
colorscheme murphy
